These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-1::.
There 4 different types of food: nectarine, peas, artichoke, garlic
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, volleyball, cricket, badminton
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, boat, bus, ship
1. the person driving the airplane is the person eating garlic##1
2. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
3. the person eating garlic is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person driving the ship##3
5. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left or right of the person eating nectarine##3
6. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1
7. the person driving the boat is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person driving the ship is between the person who's sport is badminton and the person eating nectarine##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |   2    |    3    |     4     |
| Food         | garlic      | nectarine | peas | artichoke |
| Sport   | cricket | handball  | volleyball   | badminton    |
| Transport     | airplane     | bus    | ship    | boat      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-2::.
City: paris, miami, marseilles, venice
There are 4 different nationalities: american, japanese, mexican, polish
4 different games are played: snooker, monopoly, mah-jongg, chess
1. the person playing monopoly is on the left or right of the person traveling to marseilles##3
2. the person traveling to venice is the mexican##1
3. the person traveling to marseilles is in an even position##4
4. the person playing snooker is on the far right##1
5. the person playing chess is on the far left##1
6. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the japanese##1
7. the american is between the person traveling to venice and the person traveling to miami##2
8. the polish is between the japanese and the person traveling to marseilles##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| City         | venice | marseilles   | miami | paris  |
| Nationality   | mexican     | american | polish  | japanese |
| Game     | chess        | mah-jongg  | monopoly    | snooker |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-3::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, prince, cain, montecristo
There are 4 different nationalities: american, argentine, canadian, german
4 different games are played: scrabble, canasta, billiard, bridge
1. the german is between the alhambra-smoker and the montecristo-smoker##2
2. the argentine is the person playing bridge##1
3. the person playing scrabble is the cain-smoker##1
4. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1
5. the montecristo-smoker is in an odd position##4
6. the canadian is between the prince-smoker and the american##2
7. the german is on the left of the person playing billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Cigar          | alhambra | prince   | montecristo     | cain     |
| Nationality   | argentine  | german | canadian   | american  |
| Game     | bridge      | canasta | billiard | scrabble |

