.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, disaster, horror, romance
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, dahlia, rose, daffodil
There 4 different types of food: onion, pineapple, kale, orange
1. the person who growsdaffodil is in an even position##4
2. the person watching disaster movies is the person eating pineapple##1
3. the person eating orange is on the right of the person eating onion##1
4. the person who growsdahlia is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies##3
5. the person who growsdaffodil is the person eating onion##1
6. the person watching horror movies is the person who growsmarigold##1
7. the person who growsrose is the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | crime  | romance   | horror     | disaster |
| Flower   | rose  | daffodil      | marigold        | dahlia     |
| Food         | kale | onion | orange | pineapple   |

