.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-5::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, canadian, colombian, japanese
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, comedy, martial-arts, adventure
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, dunhill, tiparillo, fonseca
1. the japanese is the person watching adventure movies##1
2. the colombian is in an odd position##4
3. the montecristo-smoker is the person watching adventure movies##1
4. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
5. the montecristo-smoker is in an even position##4
6. the person watching comedy movies is on the far left##1
7. the canadian is on the far right##1
8. the colombian is on the left or right of the tiparillo-smoker##3
9. the person watching action movies is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
| Nationality   | american   | japanese   | colombian | canadian |
| Movie-Genre         | comedy      | adventure | action      | martial-arts |
| Cigar     | dunhill | montecristo        | fonseca       | tiparillo  |

