.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, 7up, water, juice
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, havana, ritmeester, alhambra
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, guinea-pig, hamster, rat
1. the person drinking 7up is in an odd position##4
2. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
3. the owner of the chinchilla is the person drinking 7up##1
4. the person drinking water is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
5. the havana-smoker is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
7. the person drinking juice is in an even position##4
8. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4    |
| Beverage    | water   | juice      | 7up       | hot-chocolate |
| Cigar   | oliveros | alhambra | ritmeester     | havana |
| Pet     | rat     | guinea-pig  | chinchilla | hamster |

