.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, hot-chocolate, lemonade, tea
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: begonia, tulip, balloon-flower, daisy
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, german, brazilian, malaysian
1. the brazilian is the person who growsbegonia##1
2. the german is between the person who growsdaisy and the japanese##2
3. the person who growsdaisy is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the person who growstulip is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
5. the person drinking 7up is in an even position##4
6. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
7. the person who growsbegonia is the person drinking 7up##1
8. the brazilian is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage      | lemonade   | tea          | hot-chocolate | 7up        |
| Flower   | balloon-flower     | tulip | daisy   | begonia     |
| Nationality           | japanese | german         | malaysian         | brazilian |

