.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-8::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, november, may, september
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, daisy, amaryllis, begonia
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, disco, electronic, house
1. the fan of house is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
2. the person who growsamaryllis is the person who's birthday is in february##1
3. the person who growsbegonia is the person who's birthday is in may##1
4. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
5. the fan of disco is between the person who growszinnia and the person who's birthday is in february##2
6. the fan of house is on the left or right of the person who growsamaryllis##3
7. the person who's birthday is in february is in an even position##4
8. the person who's birthday is in february is between the person who's birthday is in november and the person who's birthday is in may##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Birthday         | november | february      | may       | september    |
| Flower           | daisy  | amaryllis  | begonia | zinnia |
| Music-Genre   | house      | electronic | disco         | country    |

