.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-9::.
4 different pets are kept: bird, ferret, chinchilla, mouse
The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, manager, pilot, social-worker
There are 4 different favourite colors: yellow, grey, pink, ebony
1. the entrepreneur is in an odd position##4
2. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
3. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
4. the person who likes grey is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
5. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the person who likes pink##3
6. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
7. the entrepreneur is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
8. the manager is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
9. the social-worker is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |      3       |       4       |
| Pet   | ferret         | bird  | chinchilla     | mouse         |
| Job        | social-worker | manager | entrepreneur | pilot         |
| Color      | grey         | pink  | yellow   | ebony |

