.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-10::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, drama, epic, sports
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, malaysian, nigerian, turkish
There are 4 different favourite colors: lilac, turquise, red, azure
 1. the person who likes red is on the left or right of the person watching epic movies##3
 2. the canadian is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
 4. the nigerian is between the person watching drama movies and the person watching crime movies##2
 5. the person who likes azure is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3
 6. the person who likes azure is the person watching epic movies##1
 7. the turkish is on the far right##1
 8. the person watching crime movies is in an odd position##4
 9. the malaysian is between the person watching sports movies and the person watching epic movies##2
10. the person who likes red is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | crime  | epic    | drama | sports    |
| Nationality   | canadian | nigerian | malaysian  | turkish |
| Color           | red   | azure    | lilac        | turquise   |

