.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, juice, soy-milk
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, superhero, romance, time-travel
There 4 different types of food: radish, carrot, plum, apricot
1. the person drinking 7up is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
3. the person eating apricot is on the left or right of the person watching romance movies##3
4. the person watching superhero movies is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
6. the person eating apricot is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
7. the person eating carrot is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
8. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person eating carrot##3
9. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person eating radish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage      | 7up                | soy-milk  | almond-milk | juice   |
| Movie-Genre           | time-travel | superhero | mystery   | romance |
| Food   | carrot         | radish     | apricot     | plum |

