.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-12::.
There 4 different types of food: avocado, cherry, lime, peach
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, singing, camping, reading
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, zinnia, daffodil, orchid
1. the person eating cherry is on the left of the person eating peach##1
2. the person eating lime is on the far left##1
3. the person who growszinnia is on the left or right of the person who growsorchid##3
4. the person eating lime is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
5. the person who growsamaryllis is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who growsorchid##2
6. the person who's hobby is camping is in an even position##4
7. the person eating avocado is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | lime    | cherry  | peach  | avocado |
| Hobby   | reading | singing | drawing | camping |
| Flower   | daffodil    | amaryllis     | orchid    | zinnia |

