.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-13::.
City: liverpool, hannover, hamburg, boston
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, australian, pakistani, turkish
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, tram, roller, taxi
1. the person driving the tram is between the person traveling to hamburg and the argentine##2
2. the person traveling to liverpool is on the far left or far right##3
3. the pakistani is on the left or right of the person driving the roller##3
4. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the australian##1
5. the person driving the taxi is in an odd position##4
6. the person traveling to hannover is on the left or right of the person driving the roller##3
7. the argentine is on the left or right of the turkish##3
8. the pakistani is the person traveling to liverpool##1
9. the turkish is between the person driving the roller and the person driving the skateboard##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3    |     4     |
| City      | liverpool | hamburg      | hannover  | boston    |
| Nationality   | pakistani   | australian | turkish | argentine |
| Transport           | taxi      | roller       | tram   | skateboard      |

