.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-14::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, bolivar, game, aristoff
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, sprite, cola, almond-milk
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, golf, handball, lacrosse
1. the game-smoker is in an even position##4
2. the bolivar-smoker is between the aristoff-smoker and the person who's sport is cycling##2
3. the person who's sport is golf is on the far left or far right##3
4. the aristoff-smoker is in an even position##4
5. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
6. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person who's sport is cycling and the person drinking tea##2
7. the person who's sport is golf is on the far right##1
8. the person drinking sprite is in an even position##4
9. the person who's sport is cycling is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| Cigar         | bongani    | game | bolivar  | aristoff  |
| Beverage   | cola | sprite       | almond-milk | tea |
| Sport         | handball   | cycling      | lacrosse | golf       |

