The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, coach, photographer, videographer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, mystery, satire, superhero
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, drawing, reading, baking
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is drawing is the coach##1
3. the coach is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
4. the photographer is the person watching superhero movies##1
5. the photographer is on the far left##1
6. the person watching family movies is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
7. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the videographer##1
8. the person who's hobby is baking is the videographer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |   4    |
| Job      | photographer      | coach | architect     | videographer    |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | family      | mystery | satire |
| Hobby           | reading   | drawing  | traveling     | baking |

