The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, november, february, april
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, bike, car, snowmobile
1. the aristoff-smoker is on the left or right of the bolivar-smoker##3
2. the person who's birthday is in july is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far left##1
4. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left or right of the pall-mall-smoker##3
5. the bolivar-smoker is between the person driving the bike and the person who's birthday is in february##2
6. the person driving the airplane is the person who's birthday is in april##1
7. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1
8. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Cigar    | havana    | bolivar     | aristoff    | pall-mall        |
| Birthday       | february   | july | november | april |
| Transport   | snowmobile | car      | bike    | airplane   |

