.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-17::.
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, grapefruit, lemon, tomato
There are 4 different favourite colors: aquamarine, coral, fuchsia, azure
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, hot-chocolate, fanta, juice
1. the person who likes coral is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person eating tomato##2
3. the person who likes azure is on the left or right of the person eating lemon##3
4. the person eating grapefruit is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
6. the person eating grapefruit is in an odd position##4
7. the person drinking fanta is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person eating tomato is the person who likes fuchsia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3     |    4     |
| Food          | grapefruit | tomato  | cabbage   | lemon    |
| Color   | aquamarine  | fuchsia     | azure | coral |
| Beverage   | fanta   | juice | almond-milk | hot-chocolate   |

