.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-20::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, broccoli, lime, pomegranate
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, january, april, june
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, handball, parkour, badminton
1. the person eating apple is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in june is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3
4. the person eating lime is on the far left##1
5. the person eating broccoli is between the person who's birthday is in june and the person who's birthday is in october##2
6. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
7. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person eating apple##1
8. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Food    | lime    | broccoli    | apple  | pomegranate |
| Birthday   | june | january | october | april      |
| Sport     | handball   | tennis        | badminton   | parkour       |

 